Serpentor:


Serpentor sees a robot flying overhead.  A Maximal signature eminated from 
him.
"Serpentor, terrorize!" the semi-pscyhotic Predatron's body changed around, 
excess materials from subspace adding onto his current form.  In his robot 
mode, he raised his plasma launcher.
"Like shooting a cyber duck in a barrel." he fired off a powerful plasma 
blast at Striker from below.
